thread.title: Mr. Andrews

author: Mr. Andrews
title: Mr. Andrews
text: The customer service desk is located within the airport so it's easy to find, after a short registration procedure you're given the keys and an information pack and directions to find your car. You drop the car back exactly where you picked it up, there you report to the service desk, you hand the keys back and the car is checked over ....providing there fuel tank is filled to the level you got it and there's no damage to the car your deposit is returned and that's it.
